INSERT INTO `wp_eqv5w1_comments` VALUES(44, 187, 'myvoiceofpraise', 'MyVoiceOfPraise@aim.com', 'http://myvoiceofpraise.wordpress.com/', '75.109.29.141', '2007-08-06 06:56:51', '2007-08-06 06:56:51', 'I wish I could transition as well as you do. I''m terrified of the unknown, and scared to live outside of the boundaries I''ve created on my own. But besides that, I really like what you said about Jesus knowing He only had 3 years for all His ministry, yet He never rushed. I''ve never thought about that. If Jesus never rushed, why should we. Why am I always so worried about the journey? It''s funny how much information we know, and how little of it we actually take to heart and practice. Like, how we know God always knows best yet we worry ourselves to death about every little thing that happens. We KNOW He''s got it under control and we still don''t take to heart the fact everything''s ok.\n\nAhh I''m ranting! Sorry! But, I really enjoyed this entry.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0);
