INSERT INTO `wp_eqv5w1_comments` VALUES(53, 203, 'holysoulja', 'holysoulja@gmail.com', 'http://www.myspace.com/holysouljabeats', '71.237.92.131', '2007-09-04 02:38:06', '2007-09-04 02:38:06', 'Ahhh that''s true. He has JUST been speaking the same thing to me in different terms this week. Allow me to share...\n\nBasically we are not experiencing the fullness of a real friendship with God through Christ because there are still areas in our lives that we are not willing to lay down... relationships, money, and especially control of our own lives. We still are pretty determined to be independent, but doesn''t Paul write that "you are not your own...you were bought at a price; therefore glorify God in your body and in your spirit, which are God''s." (1Cor. 6:19-20)\n\nDon''t get me wrong... I''m not being legalistic at all. I''m simply saying that we CAN be so in love with Christ that nothing else in this world could possibly be esteemed higher than Him. How? I think we''re on the right track! By truly agreeing in our heart that Christ is our "better half" :) and that He is our all in all.\n\nAh, this isn''t exactly how I intended to word all this, but it''s from the heart, so that''s what counts, right?\n\nLove ya sista lady! I''m believing that God''s gonna take you and the people you fellowship with through this transition with your hearts focused on HIM in each move you make. So that all the outward changes in appearance are not without the inward changes in the hearts!\n\nI love God.\n\nand long blogs.\n\nover and out.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0);
