rc="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3149/2695892752_56273bacd4.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="371" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><a title="Ayla by elle_effect, on Flickr" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/elle_effect/2642944969/"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3128/2642944969_7bf27b9fde.jpg" alt="Ayla" width="500" height="332" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><a title="on the road by elle_effect, on Flickr" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/elle_effect/2695890876/"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3067/2695890876_9e949dcd6e.jpg" alt="on the road" width="500" height="391" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><a title="brother sister by elle_effect, on Flickr" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/elle_effect/2695910304/"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3225/2695910304_0e46fd2014.jpg" alt="brother sister" width="500" height="332" /></a></p>\n\nÂ \n\nÂ \n<p style="text-align:center;">And even kids love Mac:</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><a title="cfo_0549 by elle_effect, on Flickr" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/elle_effect/2695910650/"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3027/2695910650_430817b5a9.jpg" alt="cfo_0549" width="500" height="332" /></a></p>', 'photos from the mountains', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'photos-from-the-mountains', '', '', '2008-07-23 13:42:46', '2008-07-23 13:42:46', '', 0, 'http://laurensusanna.wordpress.com/?p=638', 0, 'post', '', 4);
INSERT INTO `wp_eqv5w1_posts` VALUES(640, 2, '2008-07-31 02:21:47', '2008-07-31 02:21:47', 'I promised a video, and here it is:Â \n\n[vimeo video=http://vimeo.com/1439668]\n\nÂ \n\nan album of all the photos (I took) that night at the show <a href="http://www.facebook.com/album.php?aid=2000187&amp;l=32947&amp;id=1592310016">HERE</a>.\n\n<strong>We raised $500 that night!</strong>\n\nÂ \n\nI''m sure I''ll be posting more from others, too, in the near future.\n\nÂ \n\nMy family returned from Medellin, Columbia last night around midnight. Today has been a day of catching up, learning, culture shock and preparation for what''s coming next... : ) And you all won''t believe it when I tell you... <em>soon</em>.\n\nI had a senior photo shoot with Nick today that went well; photos from that tomorrow.Â \n\nTomorrow, I have a shoot with 2 dancers - Kathleen and Caitlin. Excited to do a duet shoot. It''ll turn out beautiful.\nSaturday, Caitlin, my friend Laura and I leave for Ad Deum Dance Intensive in Houston, TX. I''ll be meeting with Zach McNair and his lovely girl sometime that week for coffee and a shoot, and I''ll be reconnecting with some great people in The Woodlands at the intensive... even though I injured my leg last week in a prep class flipping/rolling over someone''s back (smart, right?), it''s much better and I''ll be taking my 9-4 daily classes in stride. Wish me luck!Â \n\nÂ \n\nPhotos and words from adventures to come soon.\n\nÂ \n\nÂ \n\nAnd I still need your help to get me to South Africa in Sept! We''re so close...Â \n\n-lauren\n\nÂ \n\nSpecial thanks to those who ate, slept and breathed this art show 2 days in preparation. I owe you more than you know. I wouldn''t have pulled it off without you! And I never want to make a kabob again! ; )', 'Benefit House Art Show -', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'benefit-house-art-show', '', '', '2008-07-31 02:21:47', '2008-07-31 02:21:47', '', 0, 'http://laurensusanna.wordpress.com/?p=640', 0, 'post', '', 2);
INSERT INTO `wp_eqv5w1_posts` VALUES(646, 2, '2008-08-01 03:22:17', '2008-08-01 03:22:17', '<p style="text-align:center;"><em>back on the road again</em>...</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://i281.photobucket.com/albums/kk213/elle_effect/meanddad02555-1.jpg" alt="" /><img src="http://i281.photobucket.com/albums/kk213/elle_effect/meincar02470.jpg" alt="" /></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">I''ve got a pretty full week ahead of me and am able to meet up with some great old friends and making a few new. If you''re in the area and would like to meet up, do dinner or a shoot, let me know. I''m free after 6.</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">(Told you my week was packed!)</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">Message me and we''ll work something out : )</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">And I''m needing to still raise funds for Africa by the end of next month! If you''re willing to help in any way, you have no idea how much it would bless my heart.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center;">See you Saturday in the hot-hot heat,\nLauren\n<p style="text-align:center;">ps: also. nashville next month for a few album shoots. contact me if you want to schedule.</p>', 'next week- houston, TX', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'next-week-houston-tx', '', '', '2008-08-01 03:22:17', '2008-08-01 03:22:17', '', 0, 'http://laurensusanna.wordpress.com/?p=646', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_eqv5w1_posts` VALUES(651, 2, '2008-08-02 00:31:03', '2008-08-02 00:31:03', '<p style="text-align:center;">Â Â  Â O God, you are my God;\nÂ Â Â Â Â Â I earnestly search for you.\nÂ Â Â My soul thirsts for you;\nÂ Â Â Â Â Â my <em>whole body</em> longs for you\nÂ Â Â in this parched and weary land\nÂ Â Â Â Â Â where there is no water.\nÂ I have seen you in your sanctuary\nÂ Â Â Â Â Â and gazed upon your power and glory.\nÂ <strong>Your unfailing love is better than life itself.</strong>\n<p style="text-align:center;">Â </p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">Â </p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">Â </p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">Â </p>', '////', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '651', '', '', '2008-08-02 00:31:03', '2008-08-02 00:31:03', '', 0, 'http://laurensusanna.wordpress.com/?p=651', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_eqv5w1_posts` VALUES(653, 2, '2008-08-02 00:53:15', '2008-08-02 00:53:15', 'This guy is going to South Africa with me:Â   Â  <img src="http://i281.photobucket.com/albums/kk213/elle_effect/n1053234231_59594_4805.jpg" alt="" /> Â   <a href="http://myspace.com/natejohnsonmusic">Nate Johnson</a>, ladies and gentlemen. I owe him 245768909 phone calls as of now full of information. Â  We''re doing the photojournalism project together - I''m stoked to be traveling and working with someone so talented...<em> Nate, you are great.</em> Â  Â Â  Â Â \n\nUpdates SOOOOON on how you can help this rad crew get to South Africa... and every person who donates now will get a free 5x7 print of one of the photos from the trip. : )Â   Â \n\nÂ \n<a href="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_donations&amp;business=elle_effect%40mac%2ecom&amp;item_name=Lauren%20Stonestreet&amp;no_shipping=0&amp;no_note=1&amp;tax=0&amp;currency_code=USD&amp;lc=US&amp;bn=PP%2dDonationsBF&amp;charset=UTF%2d8"><img src="http://i281.photobucket.com/albums/kk213/elle_effect/donate.jpg" alt="" /></a>\nÂ \n\nÂ   - lauren', 'Africa Update:', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'africa-update', '', '', '2008-08-02 00:53:15', '2008-08-02 00:53:15', '', 0, 'http://laurensusanna.wordpress.com/?p=653', 0, 'post', '', 4);
INSERT INTO `wp_eqv5w1_posts` VALUES(659, 2, '2008-08-07 01:21:57', '2008-08-07 01:21:57', 'crazy, crazy, crazy, crrrazy rad week thus far. I don''t have the time to update you just yet! But when I do - it will be quite the explosion. There have been things brewing for awhile, and they''re coming to the surface, running over and getting on everybody. You''ll understand what I mean later : )Â \n\nVideos have happened, random photos have been taken, purposeful photos have been taken, late night talks, walks to target, dancedancedance, choreography, mind-weary, heart-strong, new opportunities on the horizon very soon, new-news about South Africa (things are happening DAILY concerning this trip, it''s blowing my MIND), London is on the map for a few days in that time as well as potentially ending the trip passing through Switzerland. New-news to come soon.\n\n-Lauren\n\nPS: Funds. Still. Needed. Help me get there, ladies and gents. I need you.', 'from humid, kinda-stormy houston -', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'from-humid-kinda-stormy-houston', '', '', '2008-08-07 01:21:57', '2008-08-07 01:21:57', '', 0, 'http://laurensusanna.wordpress.com/?p=659', 0, 'post', '', 3);
INSERT INTO `wp_eqv5w1_posts` VALUES(665, 2, '2008-08-11 20:39:29', '2008-08-11 20:39:29', 'This weekend has been the longest ever. Friday I finished the intensive, Saturday I flew home from Houston, threw in laundry and crashed at 3am, woke up at 7 the next morning by two lovely people at my door - Adam and Kate. They were passing through, refueling and heading to Nashville... where I am now. I have been in 4 states in 2 days (TX, NC, WV, TN). Glorious.Â \n\nI''m sitting here updating you all a bit sitting on my friend, Laura''s, couch. I''ll have the privilege of taking photos of her this week. She''s one of the violinists at <a href="http://myspace.com/brookewaggoner">Brooke Waggoner</a>''s CD release show this Wed night... so stoked I get to go. Love her music.Â \n\nI had a shoot with <a href="http://myspace.com/adamtaylormusic">Adam</a> yesterday and I have an album shoot with a lovely artist, <a href="http://www.myspace.com/loritriplett">Lori TriplettÂ </a>this evening (great conceptual shoot). I''ve got tons of photos to sift through from last weeks <a href="http://danceaddeum.com/">dance company</a> performances... so, it looks like I''ll be having quite the photo update here soon.Â \n\nI also was able to meet, finally, my dear friend <a href="http://myspace.com/wakeupdreamer">Ali Formby</a> face-to-face. She recently moved here. Hung out on <a href="http://myspace.com/thememorytree">Brandon''s</a> front porch for most of the evening - so good to see him again.\n\nI''m trying to catch up with all that''s happened in the past few days. My body is still experiencing some jet lag and lack of sleep.Â \n\nTomorrow, I get to see my dear friend and talented musician, <a href="http://myspace.com/katherinemez">Katherine Mez</a>, play. Kindred of mine.Â \n\nWe''ll see how the rest of this week pans out. All I know is that I want to crash every night at 9PM. Ha.Â \n\nÂ \n\nGood to be back in this town, even only for a little while.\n\nIf you''d like to help me get to Africa, book a shoot with me while I''m here. ; )Â \n-lauren\nPS: weird, non-traditional partnering modern dance video coming your way soon. I''m posting it for you, Luke. Yes, you.', 'Time is Flying...', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'time-is-flying', '', '', '2008-08-11 20:39:29', '2008-08-11 20:39:29', '', 0, 'http://laurensusanna.wordpress.com/?p=665', 0, 'post', '', 0);
